                    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>How do I create an account?</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            Click on the "Sign Up" button in the top right corner and use your Chandigarh University email address to create your account. You'll need to verify your email to complete registration.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>How do I list an item for sale?</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            After logging in, click on "Sell Item" in the navigation. Fill out the form with item details, upload photos, set your price, and publish your listing.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Is there any fee for using CU Bazar?</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            No, CU Bazar is completely free for Chandigarh University students. There are no listing fees or commission charges.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>How do I contact a seller?</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            Click on the item you're interested in and use the "Contact Seller" button to send a message. The seller will be notified and can respond through the platform.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>What safety measures are in place?</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            All users are verified Chandigarh University students. We recommend meeting in public campus locations and using the campus security escort service if meeting after dark.
                        </div>
                    </div>
